  "bodyHtml": "<h1>今日原油市场每日监测报告 (2026-06-30)</h1>\n<h2>核心摘要</h2>\n<p>今日原油市场受地缘政治局势紧张影响小幅收涨。由于周末美伊在主要地区的军事冲突加剧了市场对霍尔木兹海峡航运稳定性的担忧，国际油价显著走高。截至6月29日收盘，WTI原油期货结算价上涨2.20%至70.75美元/桶，Brent原油期货结算价上涨1.61%至73.15美元/桶。虽然随后有报道指出双方同意暂停敌对行动并在多哈恢复谈判，但地缘溢价仍然为油价提供了关键支撑。</p>\n<h2>1. 价格走势</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>指标</th>\n<th>收盘价 (USD/bbl)</th>\n<th>日变动 %</th>\n<th>来源</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Brent Crude (布伦特原油)</td>\n<td>73.15</td>\n<td>+1.61%</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEWB_nTr5jrUFfg3xrgqPPYzoFl4BZVgF1ZXHZNLohXGM_TO_0v_Jx8Ypsq9oVRc9XHKl5y4hmVrJcAen6j9YxktMk-lyO8iigorTq96qJB16wLK5b_QIFqiqqEbkn2bi5PTRxuektfOJlgnC1ODXYriTYp7gPGKYM3b-UVWkxNZbSo\">来源：thestar.com.my</a>, <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGbLH0xH-l5lOrrHeej1QaH2da56BstqOBzP-_XkkbiTDkPuLttCoD_yEBLkprguaE_nsYORXxbiNC2G_gALLC1MZ3_kYqckhjIN_-iXxlD1L2XiO13o7iGu2dO8QcXLk-i9zWGr-848HRGO21-Lko1rHHvobK5REfHFei0tqAgoLL-uqaC5T_uLtqS34iOrLidSd-DJyQ_0DAUOnhI9oQuP-iHF8vd0BJfMv0FAw==\">channelnewsasia.com</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>WTI Crude (WTI原油)</td>\n<td>70.75</td>\n<td>+2.20%</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEWB_nTr5jrUFfg3xrgqPPYzoFl4BZVgF1ZXHZNLohXGM_TO_0v_Jx8Ypsq9oVRc9XHKl5y4hmVrJcAen6j9YxktMk-lyO8iigorTq96qJB16wLK5b_QIFqiqqEbkn2bi5PTRxuektfOJlgnC1ODXYriTYp7gPGKYM3b-UVWkxNZbSo\">来源：thestar.com.my</a>, <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGbLH0xH-l5lOrrHeej1QaH2da56BstqOBzP-_XkkbiTDkPuLttCoD_yEBLkprguaE_nsYORXxbiNC2G_gALLC1MZ3_kYqckhjIN_-iXxlD1L2XiO13o7iGu2dO8QcXLk-i9zWGr-848HRGO21-Lko1rHHvobK5REfHFei0tqAgoLL-uqaC5T_uLtqS34iOrLidSd-DJyQ_0DAUOnhI9oQuP-iHF8vd0BJfMv0FAw==\">channelnewsasia.com</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>2. OPEC+ 与供给侧动态</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>产量配额调整</strong>：OPEC+七个核心成员国（沙特阿拉伯、俄罗斯、伊拉克、科威特、哈萨克斯坦、阿尔及利亚和阿曼）此前于2026年6月7日同意，将7月份的集体原油生产配额提高188,000桶/日，使7月总配额达到约3583万桶/日 <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFbojzfJQnFs3IDosIuloja8BgF-mD5kueLwbX6BxuN6edi8rDVMdde10nQpsIimR-pomvvFUL8Gz8QUKYd4MaMAVWVV9ZqnjYEBt1FOGyGlNHAshK8XTWqnCbiByX2UMVyTc0Z6_ZlCuI=\">来源：opec.org</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>实际供应受阻</strong>：尽管配额有所提高，但由于美伊军事冲突导致霍尔木兹海峡航运受阻，中东海湾地区主要生产国的实际石油出口 and 生产面临实质性地缘政治中断，许多成员国的实际产量远低于官方目标 <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGrIq4cWpfnnsAYlgMCOEeCrBWfFheoKwofEzjWUUpj6Wl6aS7hDfhhe1OKW9W8eHu1gcRi9Riryndxb4ppGiYc0Si4lYVQPylH0RbHbWQIF6oCUi4NhjoEenYxC4q6lO87IdtCv0labbFTe2rlVAOVlbnH3DMVp9azk1YsBCwcrjeL2QJ3\">来源：discoveryalert.com.au</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>超产补偿延长</strong>：针对此前部分国家的超产行为，OPEC+已将超产国的补偿减产期限延长至2026年底，以维持减产协议的纪律性 <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEUn5V_hYU-jbVVWDtxQtD2LSq_IAof95nhp8QdqkLNwXC3fUqpHpdKkkYCdeHsvcPeJwCJwHxoJ54zuqkVEE4ssPaHCfTkv1gUxXXpptSc_TknYKT1UnKM1Og-5nvZKua1yDB5rg4Q\">来源：interfax.com</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3. 库存与需求</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>EIA库存变动</strong>：美国能源信息署（EIA）于2026年6月24日公布的报告显示，截至6月19日当周，美国商业原油库存大幅减少610万桶，至4.121亿桶，低于五年同期平均水平约7% <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHCFaD8TiJ1WVAoJUj3hoNagxXPU9jjRhaqnHS8PdWLzUGDbRIhZTtOtYGc7oPshCqnx__CAhRHHhH1RCF57jrZJpYvlmSXq_DbzCMfVCcQTAFqUbFgX-B_SanhambIgzOL-3pZobgRpIbB\">来源：eia.gov</a>。同时，美国炼厂产能利用率维持在96.1%的高位，日加工量约1710万桶 <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEs0iNu4cNmGD9NZ7ttxVxDNyXKgxisN9o5B-uobQ0qqOlVEfA8RQzoMzD-Vge2CqYMm1XbmLSYtH5d-xlZHX31Mc8xuyMxneHPL7sXJkawR3KsrW8YsW0Z8htF4g==\">来源：eia.gov</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>成品油累库</strong>：与原油去库相反，美国当周汽油库存增加210万桶，馏分油库存增加310万桶 <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHCFaD8TiJ1WVAoJUj3hoNagxXPU9jjRhaqnHS8PdWLzUGDbRIhZTtOtYGc7oPshCqnx__CAhRHHhH1RCF57jrZJpYvlmSXq_DbzCMfVCcQTAFqUbFgX-B_SanhambIgzOL-3pZobgRpIbB\">来源：eia.gov</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>需求预测下调</strong><ul>\n<li><strong>国际能源署 (IEA)</strong>：在6月17日发布的最新《石油市场报告》中，因中东局势导致霍尔木兹海峡受阻、燃料价格高企，IEA将2026年全球石油需求增长预测大幅下调70万桶/日，至同比下降110万桶/日，预计全年平均需求为1.033亿桶/日 <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZp2z0rqsq3VhuTHMSlRsVpIpXbfQRKdYOsydmzTjA0vY_C3kfnAG6TYtJQwQ3OzOtHJUmnxO7VWuz9zxl9BxEJv50s3NMlr-2C-sYUvCsGJIVD5Bd4kD6BJBAqh9BrKIdyq8Mm7SEFBJYPb-Y\">来源：iea.org</a>。</li>\n<li><strong>OPEC</strong>：OPEC亦在6月报告中连续第二次下调需求增长预期，预计2026年全球需求增长97万桶/日（此前预期为117万桶/日） <a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEngduyLJtCCXuUC1gnLi2CJ5TmG8AoiLKSjBVWUd1vuIRbat-a9lC6geJtn2d4_nMqxUZhebgNsAzDJPORDAk0X0ECDhApQYSzEQmv1pJtaFinnpEct-lEhj0yEtN7Uj76__hHqSnJBHed_34IiiYGzx2h1HGhVRUQ694qfyZygiBnEpo3Lgdh2039CIchJa-fn6G7uzttKthQzMhZZopXzwJE0GfxAIK2x-2fcfGD0lmHB6o=\">来源：businesstimes.com.sg</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>4. 结论与后续关注</h2>\n<h3>市场判断</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>地缘溢价仍是主导因素</strong>：虽然美伊宣布暂停敌对并启动多哈谈判，但只要霍尔木兹海峡的安全隐患未除，油价的地缘风险溢价就难以完全消退。</li>\n<li><strong>供需基本面呈疲软态势</strong>：IEA和OPEC双双下调需求预测表明，高油价正在对实体经济需求产生强烈的反噬作用。</li>\n<li><strong>宽幅震荡格局延续</strong>：原油库存去化对下行空间形成支撑，但需求衰退风险限制了上行空间，油价短期内将在地缘局势 and 基本面博弈中维持宽幅震荡。</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>后续观察点</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>多哈和平谈判进展</strong>：关注美伊能否达成实质性停火协议，这决定了地缘溢价是否会快速消退。</li>\n<li><strong>EIA最新库存报告</strong>：关注即将于7月1日公布的最新一周库存数据，验证原油去库 and 成品油累库的趋势是否延续。</li>\n<li><strong>OPEC+成员国实际产量</strong>：关注中东受灾成员国是否能在7月履行增产18.8万桶/日的计划，或者因地缘政治导致更大的实际减产。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>数据来源</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>数据源校验 </strong>: 否 (本日数据不可用，API 返回 404，已回退至 web_search 检索)</li>\n<li><strong>Web 检索</strong><ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEWB_nTr5jrUFfg3xrgqPPYzoFl4BZVgF1ZXHZNLohXGM_TO_0v_Jx8Ypsq9oVRc9XHKl5y4hmVrJcAen6j9YxktMk-lyO8iigorTq96qJB16wLK5b_QIFqiqqEbkn2bi5PTRxuektfOJlgnC1ODXYriTYp7gPGKYM3b-UVWkxNZbSo\">thestar.com.my</a> (原油收盘价格与日内波动)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGbLH0xH-l5lOrrHeej1QaH2da56BstqOBzP-_XkkbiTDkPuLttCoD_yEBLkprguaE_nsYORXxbiNC2G_gALLC1MZ3_kYqckhjIN_-iXxlD1L2XiO13o7iGu2dO8QcXLk-i9zWGr-848HRGO21-Lko1rHHvobK5REfHFei0tqAgoLL-uqaC5T_uLtqS34iOrLidSd-DJyQ_0DAUOnhI9oQuP-iHF8vd0BJfMv0FAw==\">channelnewsasia.com</a> (美伊冲突、多哈谈判与结算价)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFbojzfJQnFs3IDosIuloja8BgF-mD5kueLwbX6BxuN6edi8rDVMdde10nQpsIimR-pomvvFUL8Gz8QUKYd4MaMAVWVV9ZqnjYEBt1FOGyGlNHAshK8XTWqnCbiByX2UMVyTc0Z6_ZlCuI=\">opec.org</a> (2026年6月7日OPEC+配额决定)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGrIq4cWpfnnsAYlgMCOEeCrBWfFheoKwofEzjWUUpj6Wl6aS7hDfhhe1OKW9W8eHu1gcRi9Riryndxb4ppGiYc0Si4lYVQPylH0RbHbWQIF6oCUi4NhjoEenYxC4q6lO87IdtCv0labbFTe2rlVAOVlbnH3DMVp9azk1YsBCwcrjeL2QJ3\">discoveryalert.com.au</a> (海峡受阻导致中东供应中断)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEUn5V_hYU-jbVVWDtxQtD2LSq_IAof95nhp8QdqkLNwXC3fUqpHpdKkkYCdeHsvcPeJwCJwHxoJ54zuqkVEE4ssPaHCfTkv1gUxXXpptSc_TknYKT1UnKM1Og-5nvZKua1yDB5rg4Q\">interfax.com</a> (配额、补偿延长政策细节)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHCFaD8TiJ1WVAoJUj3hoNagxXPU9jjRhaqnHS8PdWLzUGDbRIhZTtOtYGc7oPshCqnx__CAhRHHhH1RCF57jrZJpYvlmSXq_DbzCMfVCcQTAFqUbFgX-B_SanhambIgzOL-3pZobgRpIbB\">eia.gov</a> (美国EIA库存变动，6月24日发布)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZp2z0rqsq3VhuTHMSlRsVpIpXbfQRKdYOsydmzTjA0vY_C3kfnAG6TYtJQwQ3OzOtHJUmnxO7VWuz9zxl9BxEJv50s3NMlr-2C-sYUvCsGJIVD5Bd4kD6BJBAqh9BrKIdyq8Mm7SEFBJYPb-Y\">iea.org</a> (6月17日全球需求预测报告)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEngduyLJtCCXuUC1gnLi2CJ5TmG8AoiLKSjBVWUd1vuIRbat-a9lC6geJtn2d4_nMqxUZhebgNsAzDJPORDAk0X0ECDhApQYSzEQmv1pJtaFinnpEct-lEhj0yEtN7Uj76__hHqSnJBHed_34IiiYGzx2h1HGhVRUQ694qfyZygiBnEpo3Lgdh2039CIchJa-fn6G7uzttKthQzMhZZopXzwJE0GfxAIK2x-2fcfGD0lmHB6o=\">businesstimes.com.sg</a> (OPEC 6月需求调整)</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>数据发现</h2>\n<p>数据科学家下次目录审查需要拾取的字段及本次提取到的数值\n- <code>brent_close_usd</code>: 73.15\n- <code>wti_close_usd</code>: 70.75\n- <code>opec_target_kbpd</code>: 35830\n- <code>eia_inventory_change_kb</code>: -6100</p>"
